source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT 
FlightPlanId,
DeviationReason,
AffectedItemsUnit,
AffectedItemsDeviationReasonChange,
json_value(Affect_item.value,'$."@unit"')  as AdjustmentUnit,
json_value(Affect_item.value,'$."@affectedItem"')  as AdjustmentAffectedItem,
json_value(Affect_item.value,'$."_value_"')as Adjustment,
TCreatedId,
TLoadDate,
TFileName
from [BcAdfLido].[OFP_FuelHeader_Adjustment_Stage]
cross APPLY openjson(
case when Left(Adjustment,1) ='[' 
then Adjustment 
else '['+Adjustment+']' end ,'$') as Affect_item
